{
  "stem": "428.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You want to run-- you run-- you want to run away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you have to know that things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When they come, you have to know that about 1:00, 12:30, 1 o'clock, they come in with dogs, with the German shepherds.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So you know that if you're not sleeping, you sleep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If you was awake, you're not sleeping.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You're awake.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You have something in your mind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You have something in your mind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we could talk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You couldn't organize nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't do nothing there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You were watched every step.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could run away if you were lucky, the same way when I run away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was-- it was difficult, you see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Polish people, you see, the German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I was-- when I run away, if I want to hide some place, the German couldn't recognize me that I am a Jew.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because I know the Polish language perfect, but the Polack recognized me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Polish people, a lot of them was interested the Jews shouldn't live through that war because the Germans gave them away the Jewish properties, you understand?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Polack, most of the Polish people, they was no good.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The people, like when I was hiding, you could count them on the fingers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Tell me about that family where you were hiding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That family, their name was Bielowitski.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He was a very-- he wasn't rich.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But very, very, very poor-- very, very good people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when I run away from that camp, Lemberg, Lwow, when I came back home, when I find nobody is alive, I went to him and he helped me and I was by him about two weeks sleeping on the attic.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And those-- those-- it's three girls was over there, yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
